overview: Adult entertainment studio Elegant Angel is releasing the latest volume of its annual series 'Performers Of The Year 2010'. The movie is a 2-Disc Set, featuring 7 scenes, and starring the biggest names of the year: Tori Black, Kristina Rose, Jenna Haze, Julia Ann, Kagney Linn Karter, Bobbi Starr, and "Buttwoman" Alexis Texas.
title: Performers of the Year 2010
